channel.title: I messed up Registration - Need Admin -
channel.description:
Can I get an Admin to look into this? I messed up registration because I was told to make a new account, but I messed up the email. So now I cant use that name and its my Registered Minecraft Account. I need the account that I messed up on deleted or the name removed from it to be able to play I can give you proof that It is my account that I screwed up on.
The forum user I messed up on is,
Elevations
Please remove the minecraft user: Elevationz from it, because of a screw up, I meant to link it with this account, again I screwed up.
If you need any proof of passwords ect, I can give that to you.
